                <ul>
                    <li>
                        a.       Did any of the following fields have a "Y" in the CFDB file and/or an approval or notification requirement in the Entanglement Summary: supplier change or subcontracting restrictions, place of performance, disclosure to third parties, citizenship restrictions, and security restrictions?
                        <br />
