            </li>
            <li>
                <br />
                2. Has the Offset Council approved transition/reposition of each of the parts that currently support offset requirements?
                <br />
                <input type="checkbox" @ViewBag.Checkbox35596_Yes /> Yes.
                <br />
                <input type="checkbox" @ViewBag.Checkbox35596_No /> No.
            </li>
        </ul>
    </p>
